# ============================================================
# Doc reorg (2026-06-27): the tracked design docs are reduced to the
# canonical bilingual set only —
#   docs/doc/rtl_design_spec.md / rtl_design_spec_ja.md          (RTL design spec, EN/JA)
#   docs/doc/image_processing_principles.md / *_ja.md            (image processing, EN/JA)
#   README.md / README_ja.md                                     (entry point, EN/JA)
